---
description: Client-side Supabase access, Zod validation, DTOs, and Edge Functions. Auto-attached for Supabase client and data hooks.
globs: ["**/integrations/supabase/**", "**/hooks/**/*.ts", "**/hooks/**/*.tsx"]
alwaysApply: false
