### 1.2 UI & Labeling Logic
- **Component**: `src/components/PersonalRatingButton.tsx`
- **Differentiation**:
    - Uses `isPriorityContext` derived from `status === 'pending'`.
    - If `status` is `'visited'` (or default), it enters "Quality context".
