## 2. Building Catalogue Domain

### Component 1: Database Schema

```sql
-- ============================================================
-- ENUMS
-- ============================================================

CREATE TYPE public.location_precision AS ENUM ('exact', 'approximate');

CREATE TYPE public.building_status AS ENUM (
